{
  "texts": [
    "Cross-entropy is used for multi-class classification problems, while MAE and MSE were also reported, and they are typically used for regression problems where the goal is to minimize the difference between the predicted and actual values.",
    "Activation Function determines the output of the neural network.",
    "Sigmoid activation was the most reported function and is used for binary classification problems.",
    "Softmax is used for multi-class classification problems.",
    "ReLu was also used often because of the publications that used CNNs for feature extraction."
  ]
}